// Migrated from REST handlers in backend/internal/api/rest/v1/support_tickets.go
// per .claude/plans/proto-naming-conventions.md. Conventions enforced:
//   * package proto.support_ticket.v1 + go_package suffix for dispatch
//   * service names = <Domain>Service, methods PascalCase verbs
//   * snake_case fields, no json_name annotations
//   * timestamps as string ISO-8601 (no google.protobuf.Timestamp)
//   * list response = {items, total, limit, offset} uniform envelope
