// identified by JWT (auth interceptor → UserID); tickets are addressed
// by their owner's UserID, not by any org. There is no `org_slug`.
//
// Attachment uploads now go through a 3-step presigned-URL flow instead of
// multipart REST:
//   1. CreateSupportTicket (or AddSupportTicketMessage) → ticket / message id
//   2. PresignAttachmentUpload(ticket_id, message_id?, filename, ct, size)
//      → put_url + opaque storage_key (server-generated)
