//      AssociateAttachments(ticket_id, [{storage_key, filename, mime, size}])
//      to materialize SupportTicketAttachment DB rows.
// This eliminates the multipart REST surface entirely; conventions §2.5
// (all wire is Connect-binary) is now fully enforced for this domain.

